      "span_text": "An improvement of influenza vaccination response by zinc was not confirmed in another study in which zinc was administered together with arginine, but the relatively high dose of zinc used in this case (zinc sulfate, 400 mg per day = 90 mg elemental zinc) might have suppressed T cell help."
